[[Translation:en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Service interval road vehicles]]
With this feature, you can set the number of days a road vehicle will wait since its last service before it will go to a depot to be serviced again. This can also be set to '''disabled''', then you can add go to depot orders allowing you to have better control over when a road vehicle is serviced.
